title: Grateful Dead Live at Desert Sky Pavilion on 1994-03-04
taper: DATs provided to KXCI's Dead Air program by Dick Latvala for broadcast in April of 1999.
description:
Set I
Mississippi Half Step Uptown Toodleloo
Little Red Rooster
Ramble On Rose
Me & My Uncle >
Big River
Bird Song
Promised Land
Set II
Iko Iko
Looks Like Rain
Crazy Fingers >
Estimated Prophet >
Drums >
Space >
I Need A Miracle >
Black Peter >
Throwing Stones
U.S. Blues


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
